          "machine_learning",
          "machineLearning",
          "MACHINE_LEARNING"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "\\b[A-Za-z0-9]{32,50}\\b",
        "message": "Pinecone API key detected in alphanumeric format. Pinecone provides vector database services for machine learning applications. Exposed API keys grant full access to create/delete indexes, manipulate vector data, query embeddings, and consume API resources. This can lead to data breaches of ML models, unauthorized access to vector embeddings, service disruption, and financial loss through quota abuse. Immediately rotate keys and implement secure storage practices.",
